# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your key, then publish/build.
# EXPO_PUBLIC_ vars are inlined into the app bundle at build/update time.
#
# Coach: without this the Coach runs in scripted "Demo" mode. With it, the
# Coach uses the live Claude API. NOTE: EXPO_PUBLIC_ vars ship inside the
# client bundle and are extractable — fine for personal testing, but for a
# public release move the key behind a small server/proxy.
EXPO_PUBLIC_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
